This folder (e.g. fnurpel_fensalir_env_se_tn_gride_hs) is assumed to be named
according the pattern
  <composite>_fensalir_env_<country code>_<site abreviation>_<security domain>
that is
  fnurpel_fensalir_env_se_tn_gride_hs
is intended for the composite "fnurpel" and configured for country "se", site
"tn", and security domain "gride_hs" (any slases are replaced with '_').

The file
  dot.fensalirenvironment
should be renamed as
  .fensalirenvironment
